          <para styleclass="VariableName" style="text-align:right;">Notes : </para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Table">A <text styleclass="Element">Circle</text> is a <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Sketch-Loop" styleclass="VariableName">sketch-loop</link>.</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table">A <text styleclass="Element">Circle</text> is the most basic shape of a <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Follower-Profile-Shape" styleclass="VariableName">Follower-Profile</link>.</para>
